{"tid":200578,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朝副外長：可隨時進行核試","createTime":"2017-04-14T05:43:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T05:43:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e7b654aac57c2bcc4740cc1cdcf2e1ff5181d0f","tid":200578,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T05:43:04.000Z","msg":"朝副外長：可隨時進行核試<br />\n<br />\n北韓副外長韓成烈表示，朝鮮半島局勢已經成為惡性循環。 韓成烈在平壤接受美聯社專訪時警告，只要最高領袖金正恩下令，可隨時進行核試，又指若果美國發動先發制人的攻擊，北韓不會坐視不理。 他又批評美國總統特朗普上任後對北韓政策，變得更惡毒和更具侵略性，透過在社交網站留言，加劇區內緊張局勢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1325209-20170414.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1325209-20170414.htm&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdYsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=66f2e52b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1325209-20170414.htm&h=18458343\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1325209-20170414.htm</a>"}]}